Description:Test puzzle for replaying a lifelink damage loop from the commander combo list: Walking Ballista plus Heliod, Sun-Crowned. First activate Heliod to give Walking Ballista lifelink. Then record one cycle: remove a +1/+1 counter from Walking Ballista targeting the opponent, then target Walking Ballista with Heliod's life-gain trigger. Repeat that recorded cycle until the opponent is defeated.

